node.text: Taking my daughter Mia for her first ever Hypercar ride and in none other than the @koenigsegg Agera RS with the 1MW package which give the cars 1360 HP.  Thanks to my friend Raymond for letting me take his car so give him a follow @srautogroup  #dailydrivenexotics #srautogroup #koenigsegg #agerars

node.text: We attended the first Burnyard bash of 2020 at @thehoonigans Irwindale location. Everyone was going off and doing insane stunts. It was our turn and we did the worlds first Lamborghini front bumper to K-rail standing burnout till the back of the car bust into flames igniting all the hot rubber!! It was epic.
